<p>太平洋投资管理公司全球经济顾问约阿希姆·费尔斯（Joachim Fels）表示:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">“我们已经</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">触及</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">这轮</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">上涨</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">行情</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">顶峰</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">从现在开始，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">经济复苏的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">势头会减</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">弱</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">。”</span></strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">“我们已经</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">触及</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">这轮</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">上涨</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">行情</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">顶峰</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">从现在开始，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">经济复苏的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">势头会减</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">弱</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">。”</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200909/2fae940d329346678567d0bf23292d03.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
